title: What about a park in the society?
description: I was thinking about a park that should be designed in the sector A, exactly on the local ground. Currently it's a really bad place for children as well as for adults. I was more of thinking about a place where we can go to walk in the morning and get some exercise? What you people think?

title: My grant father is very sick, kindly pray for him.
description: It's day 3 since my grant father is not feeling well. We have taken him to holy family, rawalpindi but his condition is very weak. It's a request to all those who are reading it to pray for him. Thanks.
